<table BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=70%><tr>
<td VALIGN=TOP bgcolor=ffffff class=itemtable>
<font face=Arial size=-1 color=black><div class=titlebar>The Marble Zone</div>

<div class=itemtext><center><br><img src=/sonichq/images/screenshots/sonicdrift/sd1marble.jpg></center>
<P>This zone is pretty straighforward as well but isn't as easy as the first one.  Look for monitors in the road such as turbo boosts, invincibility, and jump springs. THEY WILL HELP. Also be sure to keep a look out for poles and such that will sit closer into the road - They ARE an annoyance. This zone is best used if working with Sonic.<a name=z3><br><br></div></font></td></tr></table>

