<table BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=70%><tr>
<td VALIGN=TOP bgcolor=ffffff class=itemtable>
<font face=Arial size=-1 color=black><div class=titlebar>Scrap Brain Zone</div>

<div class=itemtext><center><br><img src=/sonichq/images/screenshots/sonicdrift/sd1scrapbrain.jpg></center>
<P>This isn't extremely hard but it isnt exactly easy either. Curves get in your way A LOT not to mention that in those curves you'll need to avoid the energy filtrators taht sit at the side of the road! Keep up a good pace but be mindful of your surroundings!<br><br></div></font></td></tr></table>

